criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  clinical diagnosis of COPD according to the Global Initiative for Chronic Obstructive
     Lung Disease (GOLD) criteria;

  -  ≥ 18 years old;

  -  clinical stability for 1 month prior to the study (no hospital admissions,
     exacerbations or changes in medication);

  -  able to provide their own informed consent.

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  presence of concomitant respiratory diseases;

  -  presence of severe psychiatric conditions;

  -  presence of severe neurologic/ musculoskeletal conditions and/or unstable
     cardiovascular disease.
